Class WOWZBroadcastConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.configuration.WOWZMediaConfig

    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<WOWZMediaConfig>

    public class WOWZBroadcastConfig
extends WOWZStreamConfig
    The WOWZBroadcastConfig class provides configuration properties for a live streaming broadcast.
